source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_00<tab>Narujj Boh is exhausted by his stubborn kin's single-mindedness.
TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_01<tab>Narujj Boh tiredly explains that the Amalj'aa in Zanr'ak have constructed yet more of their ominous flame-topped towers. Find the infernal beacons and destroy them.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_01<tab>Narujj Boh vous explique que les ennemis de la Ligue ont installé de nouvelles <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF207550302 /var> pour leurs rites dédiés à Ifrit. Il vous demande de détruire ces deux <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF207550302 /var>.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_02<tab>You have destroyed the infernal beacons. Return to the Ring of Ash and report to Narujj Boh.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez détruit les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF207550302 /var>. Retournez faire un rapport à Narujj Boh.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_03<tab>Narujj Boh deduces from the stink of ruin that you were successful in your task. He exults in the defeat of his enemies' plans, and thanks you for your contributions to the Brotherhood's cause.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_SEQ_03<tab>Narujj Boh vous montre plus de respect de jour en jour, et est visiblement ravi de vous avoir à ses côtés dans la Ligue. Soyez toujours à l'affût d'une autre occasion de venir en aide à vos compagnons.
TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_TODO_01<tab>Faire un rapport à Narujj Boh

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_000<tab>Our fanatic kin are nothing if not persistent. Once more they seek to focus and intensify the blessings of their deity.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_000<tab>Risible obstination que celle des pleutres de Zanr'ak<var 1D /var>! D'attiser la flamme du Dieu des flammes infernales, ils continuent. Sa protection, ils espèrent grâce à ce brasier encore plus intense renforcer. Par leurs propres moyens, ils ne cherchent pas à se défendre. Abject, un tel com<var 16 /var>por<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment est.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_001<tab>They have constructed sturdy beacons in Zanr'ak, and consecrated these towering talismans with Ifrit's fire.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_001<tab>D'énormes flambeaux, ils ont nouvellement mis en place près de Zanr'ak. Un rite spécial avec ces flammes sacrées, ils préparent.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_002<tab>You will need more than a handful of ash to smother such roaring flames, honored ally. The time for subtlety has passed! Use whatever weapons you have at your disposal, but bring these structures crashing down!
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_002<tab>Ô puissant<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var><var 1D /var>! Les symboles de l'outrecuidance des pleutres, ces <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF207550302 /var> sont<var 1D /var>! Les détruire, nous devons sans hésiter<var 1D /var>! À toi, cette mission incombe.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_004<tab>As ever, the Flamefangs will seek to deny you at every turn. Engage them if you must, but do not lose sight of your true task.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_004<tab>Ces édifices, les Crocs de Feu protègent cependant. De prudence, tu devras faire preuve.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_010<tab>Find the infernal beacons in Zanr'ak, and leave of them nothing but smoking ruin!
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_010<tab>Ces <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF207550302 /var>, nous devons détruire<var 1D /var>! Près de Zanr'ak, elles se trouvent.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_020<tab>I judge by the smell of smoke and blood that your task was a success. Even my stubborn kin must now feel a flicker of doubt in the strength their vaunted blessings bestow upon them.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_020<tab>Les flambeaux emblématiques de l'arrogance de nos ennemis, tu as détruit<var 1D /var>! Du beau travail, tu as fait. De joie, tes prouesses me remplissent.

source: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_021<tab>You, an outsider, have accomplished much for the Brotherhood. We are fortunate indeed to have you as our honored ally.
target: TEXT_BANAMA210_01241_NARUJIBOH_000_021<tab>Un<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> guerri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> de talent, tu es décidément. Une chance pour notre peuple, notre rencontre est.
